{"tid":1727420,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 抗爭方程式 ] 勇武過後，政府玩民意戰，咁我地咪玩返大遊行攞返個主動權囉！","createTime":"2019-11-16T12:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T17:00:12.000Z","uid":20272,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"860e55d76b95881142ce5cd73a6c602d3fa9bf75","tid":1727420,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMYsNct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMYsNct.png&h=4a99210e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖大家唔記得咗？<br />\n去到依一刻當然未能完全再套落現實，但其實邏輯一樣。<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得因為之前遊行俾popo反對哂，<br />\n三罷聲先響起，set roadblock被罷工 亦極受民意支持。<br />\n<br />\n加埋中大之戰，依家玩咗一個星期rb三罷，如果大家驚政府玩放任民意戰，其實我地即刻再申請返個大遊行咪得。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之依家條formula就要tune到以下咁：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">武力鎮壓和理非-&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武RB停罷之戰-&gt;</span>民意牌-&gt;<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">申請和理非遊行-&gt;</span>武力/強硬鎮壓和理非-&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武rb停罷之戰.......</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"84c31077cd8b90faf00d62c08000341a7ac15dea","tid":1727420,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1822b012aed30904991daa3ad5f0107ecd78e1f","tid":1727420,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:19:24.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=4a207c1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=0434a988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"21cf508d342766dedd516dd25bebf73605be07ee","tid":1727420,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:19:34.000Z","msg":"mon post狗不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a48388ef4840bdfd9ed71eeabc64bc2c70ed21","tid":1727420,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1822b012aed30904991daa3ad5f0107ecd78e1f","tid":1727420,"uid